ReadCaseCaseAssignment
data.value: select * from ( select distinct T1.NUMB from CKT_CASE T1 with(readuncommitted) where exists ( select * from CKT_LEG_ACT_CAS_RL T3 with(readuncommitted) where T1.NUMB = T3.CAS_NUMBER and @lgaId = T3.LGA_ID ) ) S1 cross apply ( select top(1) REASON_CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, SPD_ID, OFF_ID, OSP_CODE, OSP_DATE, CAS_NO from CKT_ASSIGN_CASE with(readuncommitted) where S1.NUMB = CAS_NO and DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate and EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate ) S2

data.name: ReadCseOrganization

data.name: ReadLegalActionLegalActionIncomeSource
data.value: select * from ( select LEGAL_ACTION_ID, ACTION_TAKEN, STANDARD_NO, CREATED_TSTAMP, TRB_ID from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION with(readuncommitted) where ACTION_TAKEN = 'ORDIWO2' and (CREATED_TSTAMP between cast(@timestamp1 as datetime2) and cast(@timestamp2 as datetime2)) and LEGAL_ACTION_ID > @legalActionId ) S1 cross apply ( select top(1) CSP_NUMBER, LGA_IDENTIFIER, ISR_IDENTIFIER, IDENTIFIER from CKT_LEGAL_ACT_ISRC with(readuncommitted) where S1.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = LGA_IDENTIFIER ) S2 order by S1.LEGAL_ACTION_ID
